# Sub-agent isolated worktrees (Agent tool with `isolation: worktree`).
# Each agent gets its own .claude/worktrees/agent-<id>/ checkout that is
# auto-cleaned at the end of the agent run; we don't want git to track them
# while they exist.
.claude/worktrees/

# Per-session kaizen scratch file. Maintained during a task, consumed by
# /after-task-dantotsus once the work merges. Local-only by design.
KAIZEN.md
